title: Does Russ Make the Broncos a Contender?
description:
Jalen & Jacoby discuss if Kyrie's 50-point night in Charlotte changed their minds about the East. Russell Wilson got traded to Denver, but are the Broncos true contenders in a stacked AFC? What should we expect when Ben Simmons returns to Philly on Thursday? Would it be smart for the Panthers to trade Christian McCaffrey? AND Aaron Rodgers is sticking with the Packers, but is Green Bay the best place for him to win?
